Name: Laser Paddles
About the game: Laser Paddles is a pong game where you can destroy your opponent's paddle or have your own paddle destroyed. Lasers are blasted, power ups are activated, balls go crazy, and sometimes even explode. Play single player against the computer, or battle against a friend with local multiplayer.
